<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>161</hymn_number>
<title>THANGTHAT U! THANGTHAT U! CH161</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Lawm u, Lawm u, Kan dawtmi Khamhtu Bawi Jesuh, Leicung mi nih Amah
 lianhnak sa u, Vanmi zong nih Jesuh lianhnak kha thangthat u, Amah
 dawtnak le velngeihnak chim u; Tuukhal bangin a mi kha a zohkhenh hna, A
 ban chungah chun nitlak a pom hna. Lawm u, Lawm u, Kan dawtmi Khamhtu
 Bawi Jesuh! Amah lawmhnak zungzal hla in sa u!

[V2]
 Lawm u, Lawm u, Kan dawtmi Khamhtu Bawi Jesuh, Kan sual ca hrengkhenh
 sifahnak a in, Kan fehnak zungzal kan hngatchannak kha a si, An thah
 cangmi Jesuh kha va bia u, Kan sifahnak a ingmi Jesuh lawm u, Amah
 dawtnak lawmh cawk loin a tam. Lawm u, Lawm u, Kan dawtmi Khamhtu Bawi
 Jesuh! Amah lawmhnak zungzal hla in sa u!

[V3]
 Lawm u, Lawm u, Kan dawtmi Khamhtu Bawi Jesuh, Vancung khua ah Amah
 thawng kha a ngan, Jesuh Khamhbawi zungzal in zungzal tiang a uk,
 Siangpahrang, Bawi, Profet, Tlangbawi a si, A rat tikah vawlei kha a pen
 dih lai, Lianhnak, Sunparnak, Bawipa ta an si. Lawm u, Lawm u, Kan dawtmi
 Khamhtu Bawi Jesuh! Amah lawmhnak zungzal hla in sa u!.</lyrics>
<key>Ab</key>
</song>